                    "line_text": "Qui vacille en bas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Sent que sa patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Est là-bas ! là-bas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Prends donc sur ton aile\nMon âme avec toi ;\nMon âme éternelle\nEst lasse de moi.\nMon âme flétrie\nQui vacille en bas,\nSent que sa patrie\nEst là-bas ! là-bas !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Prends-donc… mais que dis-je !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5",
